Acceptance Criteria
	‚Ä¢	A search field allows search by:
	‚Ä¢	UID
	‚Ä¢	First name
	‚Ä¢	Last name
	‚Ä¢	The technician can select one collaborator from the results
	‚Ä¢	The selected collaborator becomes the target owner for the process

